<template>
    <v-container fluid>
        <v-row align="center" justify="center">
            <v-col cols="10">
                <v-file-input
                    show-size
                    small-chips
                    multiple
                    accept=".xml"
                    label="XML file input"
                    v-model="files"
                />
            </v-col>
            <v-btn text small @click="onUploadClick()">upload</v-btn>
        </v-row>
    </v-container>
</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";
export default {
    name: "Main",
    data: () => ({
        files: [],
    }),
    methods: {
        onUploadClick() {
            console.log(this.files);

            this.axios
                .post("localhost:8080/api/convert/xml/", this.files[0])
                .then((response) => console.log(response));
        },
    },
};
</script>
